          "blocks": {
            "caption": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Setting 02</p>",
                "type_preset": "h6"
              }
            },
            "heading": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<h2>Summer Garden Entertaining</h2>",
                "type_preset": "h3"
              }
            },
            "body": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>The evening's warm. The doors are open. The garden table is set for six. This is where Lettii lamps earn their place — no extension cables running across the lawn, no candles blowing out, no plastic solar stakes. IP54 waterproof means you leave them out even if the weather turns. One charge, one entire evening outside.</p>",
                "type_preset": "rte",
                "max_width": "narrow"
              }
            },
            "cta": {
              "type": "button",
              "settings": {
                "label": "Shop Garden & Outdoor",
                "link": "/collections/garden-outdoor",
                "style_class": "link"
              }
            }
          },
          "block_order": ["caption", "heading", "body", "cta"]
        }
      },
      "settings": {
        "media_position": "right",
        "media_width": "wide",
        "media_height": "60svh",
        "section_width": "full-width",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
